msgctxt "MainWindow|"
msgid ""
"While Mozhi acts as a proxy to protect your privacy, the third-party "
"services it uses may store and analyze the text you send. Your instance "
"right now is '%1', but you can change it in the translation settings. See "
"instance details in the link above."
msgstr ""
"Mozhik zure pribatutasuna babesteko proxy gisa jarduten duen arren, "
"erabiltzen dituen hirugarrenen zerbitzuek bidaltzen duzun testua gorde eta "
"aztertu dezakete. Une honetan zure instantzia '%1' da, baina itzulpen-"
"ezarpenetan alda dezakezu. Ikusi kasuaren xehetasunak goiko estekan."

